column1: # The 1910s sheet is shared with the Low Hall site. The gauge and observer moved to Hungate Hall from Low Hall in November 1910.
# The 1933 total has been reduced by 0.03 compared to the sheet figure to match the sum of the months.
# The final October 1939 figure is shown bracketed and has been omitted.
# Hungate Hall was renamed Houndgate Hall in 1936; its modern address is 20 Hungate.
